        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "BGE M3 shows lower latency and higher throughput in self-hosted environments, making it suitable for real-time applications. OpenAI embeddings excel in ease of use but may incur higher costs at scale. Benchmark your specific workload to validate these metrics."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "API Integration and Implementation Strategies"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrate BGE M3 using frameworks like Hugging Face Transformers or custom Docker containers for full control. For OpenAI, leverage their REST API with proper error handling and rate limiting. Key steps include:"
          }
